c: 14
v: 26
t: "wmthl kalimat khabithat -why kalimat alkfr- kashajarat khabithat almakl walmtem, wahi shajaratan alhnzl, aqtlet mn aela alard; li'ana erwqha qaribat min sath al'ard ma laha 'asl thabt, wala fre saed, wkdhlk alkafir la thubat lah wala khayr fyh, wala yurfae lah eamal salih 'iilaa allh"